  "description": "This ‘poshed-up' bacon and mushroom pizza is sure to be a hit with all ages. Simple too – you'll just top naan with a speedy homemade tomato sauce, torn mozzarella, crumbled baby chestnut mushrooms and herby pancetta. The finishing touch? Dollops of basil pesto and a rocket and cherry tomato salad. Pizza time!",
